org.jsimpledb.util

  • Packages that use org.jsimpledb.util 
    Package Description
    org.jsimpledb.cli
    JSimpleDB Command Line Interface (CLI) classes.
    org.jsimpledb.cli.cmd
    JSimpleDB CLI Command related classes, including pre-defined commands.
    org.jsimpledb.core
    Core classes for the JSimpleDB Java persistence layer.
    org.jsimpledb.core.type
    JSimpleDB FieldTypes.
    org.jsimpledb.core.util
    JSimpleDB core API utility classes.
    org.jsimpledb.jsck.cmd
    CLI commands associated with Jsck, the JSimpleDB key/value database consistency checker.
    org.jsimpledb.kv
    byte[] array key/value store API and related utility classes.
    org.jsimpledb.kv.array
    A simple KVStore implementation based on a sorted array of key/value pairs.
    org.jsimpledb.kv.bdb
    KVDatabase implementation based on Oracle's Berkeley DB Java Edition.
    org.jsimpledb.kv.caching
    Caching KVStore and KVDatabase layers.
    org.jsimpledb.kv.fdb
    KVDatabase implementation based on FoundationDB.
    org.jsimpledb.kv.leveldb
    KVDatabase implementation based on LevelDB.
    org.jsimpledb.kv.mvcc
    Utility classes for MVCC type operations using a KVStore.
    org.jsimpledb.kv.raft
    A distributed KVDatabase based on the Raft consensus algorithm.
    org.jsimpledb.kv.raft.cmd
    Raft-related CLI Commands.
    org.jsimpledb.kv.rocksdb
    KVDatabase implementation based on RocksDB.
    org.jsimpledb.kv.simple
    A simple in-memory implementation of the KVDatabase interface.
    org.jsimpledb.kv.spanner
    KVDatabase implementation based on Google Cloud Spanner.
    org.jsimpledb.kv.sql
    KVDatabase implementations based on SQL connections.
    org.jsimpledb.kv.util
    Utility classes relating to the KVDatabase interface.
    org.jsimpledb.parse
    JSimpleDB parsing related classes.
    org.jsimpledb.parse.expr
    Classes for parsing Java expressions with JSimpleDB-specific extensions.
    org.jsimpledb.parse.func
    Function used in a ParseSession, including built-ins.
    org.jsimpledb.parse.util
    JSimpleDB parsing utility classes.
    org.jsimpledb.schema
    Classes for modeling JSimpleDB Database schemas.
    org.jsimpledb.util
    General utility classes used with JSimpleDB.
